Proposal of Categories to Classify Cannon Cameras /!/ Learning to differentiate the number of Canon Cameras has been a nightmare. After a few months I think I've finally deciphered the classification, and found... there is just too many!

&amp;#x200B;

This is my formal proposal to Canon to market their Cameras, Three categories, Two Types, Two sensors. This could make easier to select which camera you need.

&amp;#x200B;

Your comments are more than welcome

